*
 * 热更新替换
 * 1. custom/hotAssets/version.conf version.conf 进行比较
 * 2. 如果是新的则进行替换
 * 3. cp -Rf custom/hotAssets/static/* src/app/public
 * 4. cp -Rf custom/hotAssets/views/* src/webapp/views
 * 5. 替换config.appConfig.commit
